<h2 class="text-heading1 omd:text-heading1 font-semibold text-text-primary" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 16px 0px 8px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.01em; color: var(--text-color); word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">&igrave;m hiểu chung&nbsp;ung thư phổi</h2>
<div style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; word-break: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 8px;">
<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 18px; word-break: break-word; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 24px; margin: 12px !important 0px 8px 0px;">Ung thư phổi l&agrave; g&igrave;?&nbsp;</h3>
<p dir="ltr" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 24px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word;">Ung thư phổi l&agrave; một bệnh l&yacute; &aacute;c t&iacute;nh trong đ&oacute; c&aacute;c tế b&agrave;o bất thường trong phổi nh&acirc;n l&ecirc;n một c&aacute;ch mất kiểm so&aacute;t, dẫn đến h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh một hay nhiều c&aacute;c &nbsp;khối ung thư. Qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y bắt đầu từ phổi, nơi bao gồm kh&iacute; quản, phế quản gốc, c&aacute;c phế quản, tiểu phế quản... nhỏ hơn trong nhu m&ocirc; phổi đến tận phế nang, nơi trao đổi oxy v&agrave; carbon dioxide (CO2). C&aacute;c tế b&agrave;o ung thư c&oacute; thể h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh khối u &aacute;c, di căn đến c&aacute;c cơ quan, bộ phận kh&aacute;c của cơ thể.</p>
<p dir="ltr" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 24px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word;">C&oacute; hai loại ch&iacute;nh của ung thư phổi:</p>
<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 1em 24px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; padding: 0px; word-break: break-word;">
<li dir="ltr" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; word-break: break-word; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 8px;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration: inherit; word-break: break-word; cursor: pointer;" href="https://nhathuoclongchau.com.vn/bai-viet/ung-thu-phoi-te-bao-nho-la-gi-51532.html">Ung thư phổi tế b&agrave;o nhỏ</a>&nbsp;(Small cell lung cancer - SCLC): Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; dạng &iacute;t phổ biến hơn, nhưng tiến triển nhanh v&agrave; thường di căn nhanh ch&oacute;ng. Loại n&agrave;y thường gặp tr&ecirc;n những người h&uacute;t thuốc nhiều, l&acirc;u năm.&nbsp;</li>
<li dir="ltr" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; word-break: break-word; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 8px;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration: inherit; word-break: break-word; cursor: pointer;" href="https://nhathuoclongchau.com.vn/bai-viet/ung-thu-phoi-khong-te-bao-nho-la-gi-va-bieu-hien-som-cua-benh-51508.html">Ung thư phổi kh&ocirc;ng tế b&agrave;o nhỏ</a>&nbsp;(Non-small cell lung cancer - NSCLC): Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; dạng phổ biến nhất của ung thư phổi, chiếm khoảng 85% c&aacute;c trường hợp. NSCLC bao gồm: Ung thư biểu m&ocirc; tuyến, ung thư biểu m&ocirc; tế b&agrave;o vảy, v&agrave; ung thư biểu m&ocirc; tế b&agrave;o lớn.</li>
</ul>
<p dir="ltr" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 24px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word;">Ung thư phổi gặp cả tr&ecirc;n nam v&agrave; nữ giới. Mặc d&ugrave; tỷ lệ mắc, tử vong do ung thư phổi c&oacute; thể kh&aacute;c nhau giữa c&aacute;c giới v&agrave; c&aacute;c nh&oacute;m d&acirc;n cư kh&aacute;c nhau. Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n ch&iacute;nh g&acirc;y ra ung thư phổi l&agrave; h&uacute;t thuốc, b&ecirc;n cạnh đ&oacute; c&ograve;n c&oacute; c&aacute;c yếu tố kh&aacute;c như tiếp x&uacute;c với h&oacute;a chất radon, amiăng, &ocirc; nhiễm kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute;...</p>
<p dir="ltr" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 24px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; word-break: break-word;">Xem th&ecirc;m:&nbsp;</em><a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration: inherit; word-break: break-word; cursor: pointer;" href="https://nhathuoclongchau.com.vn/bai-viet/co-may-loai-ung-thu-phoi.html"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rota