<div style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; word-break: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text-color); font-weight: 400; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 8px;">
<p dir="ltr" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 24px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word;">Để gi&uacute;p cho việc lựa chọn hướng điều trị v&agrave; đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute; khả năng hồi phục cũng như ti&ecirc;n lượng t&igrave;nh trạng bệnh, c&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n gia đ&atilde; chia mức độ tiến triển của khối u th&agrave;nh 4 giai đoạn. Gồm:</p>
