<h2 class="text-heading1 omd:text-heading1 font-semibold text-text-primary" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 16px 0px 8px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.01em; color: var(--text-color); word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">T&igrave;m hiểu chung&nbsp;tim đập nhanh</h2>
<div style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; word-break: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 8px;">
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 24px; color: var(--text-color); overflow-wrap: break-word;">Tim đập nhanh (Tachycardia) l&agrave; khi tim đập nhanh hơn nhiều so với b&igrave;nh thường, thường l&agrave; hơn 100 nhịp mỗi ph&uacute;t. Nhịp tim nhanh c&oacute; thể l&agrave; phản ứng b&igrave;nh thường của cơ thể trước những nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng phải do bệnh l&yacute; hoặc cũng c&oacute; thể l&agrave; b&aacute;o động của một bệnh l&yacute; nguy hiểm.&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration: inherit; word-break: break-word; cursor: pointer;" href="https://nhathuoclongchau.com.vn/bai-viet/roi-loan-nhip-tim-nhanh-tren-that-nguyen-nhan-va-cach-dieu-tri-hieu-qua.html">Nhịp tim nhanh tr&ecirc;n thất</a>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-