<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #020b27; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: __Inter_6493b6, __Inter_Fallback_6493b6; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; font-weight: bolder; word-break: break-word;">Giai đoạn nguy hiểm (ng&agrave;y thứ 3 đến ng&agrave;y thứ 7):</span>&nbsp;Bệnh nh&acirc;n vẫn c&ograve;n sốt hoặc giảm sốt. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c&oacute; c&aacute;c triệu chứng như đau bụng, chủ yếu ở v&ugrave;ng gan, gan to tr&ecirc;n 2cm v&agrave; men gan tăng cao. Xuất hiện n&ocirc;n mửa, xuất huyết dưới da, ni&ecirc;m mạc, chảy m&aacute;u cam nặng, v&agrave; c&oacute; thể xuất huyết đa cơ quan. Trong trường hợp nặng, bệnh nh&acirc;n c&oacute; thể bị suy tạng v&agrave; rối loạn tri gi&aacute;c.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #020b27; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: __Inter_6493b6, __Inter_Fallback_6493b6; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; font-weight: bolder; word-break: break-word;">Giai đoạn hồi phục:&nbsp;</span>Bệnh nh&acirc;n hạ sốt hoặc ngừng sốt, huyết động ổn định, sức khỏe cải thiện,&nbsp;<a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration: inherit; word-break: break-word; cursor: pointer;" href="https://nhathuoclongchau.com.vn/benh/phat-ban-884.html">ph&aacute;t ban</a>&nbsp;hồi phục hoặc chỉ c&ograve;n ngứa nhẹ ngo&agrave;i da.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #020b27; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: __Inter_6493b6, __Inter_Fallback_6493b6; background-color: #ffffff;">Nếu kh&ocirc;ng được điều trị kịp thời, sốt xuất huyết c&oacute; thể g&acirc;y ra nhiều biến chứng nghi&ecirc;m trọng như sốc do mất m&aacute;u, xuất huyết tạng (xuất huyết ti&ecirc;u ho&aacute;, xuất huyết n&atilde;o), suy đa tạng (<a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration: inherit; word-break: break-word; cursor: pointer;" href="https://nhathuoclongchau.com.vn/benh/suy-gan-617.html">suy gan</a>, suy thận, vi&ecirc;m cơ tim, suy tim) v&agrave; tử vong.</p>
<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 16px 0px 8px; font-size: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #020b27; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-family: __Inter_6493b6, __Inter_Fallback_6493b6; background-color: #ffffff;">Vắc xin sốt xuất huyết hoạt động thế n&agrave;o để ph&ograve;ng bệnh?</h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; margin: 8px 0px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #020b27; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: __Inter_6493b6, __Inter_Fallback_6493b6; background-color: #ffffff;"><a style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid #e5e7eb; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 #0000; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration: inherit; word-break: break-word; cursor: pointer;" href="https://nhathuoclongchau.com.vn/vac-xin-sot-xuat-huyet">Qdenga</a>&nbsp;l&agrave; vắc xin ph&ograve;ng ngừa sốt xuất huyết đầu ti&ecirc;n được cấp ph&eacute;p lưu h&agrave;nh tại Việt Nam. Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; vắc xin chứa virus Dengue sống giảm độc lực, hoạt động bằng c&aacute;ch nh&acirc;n l&ecirc;n tại chỗ v&agrave; tạo ra đ&aacute;p ứng miễn dịch dịch thể lẫn miễn dịch tế b&agrave;o, gi&uacute;p cơ thể chống lại cả 4 type huyết thanh của virus Dengue.</p>
